---
import MainLayout from "../layout/MainLayout.astro";
import TheHeader from "../components/theHeader.astro";
import Menu from "../components/menu.astro";
import PhilosophySection from "../components/philosophySection.astro";
import PauseSection from "../components/pauseSection.astro";
import ContactSection from "../components/contactSection.astro";
import PortfolioHero from "../components/portfolioHero.astro";
import PortfolioBigOne from "../components/portfolioBigOne.astro";
import PortfolioTwoImages from "../components/portfolioTwoImages.astro";
---

<MainLayout MainTitle="Fidel Hernandez :: Majestic Jade Project" MainDescription="Jade is a Mexican event coordination agency dedicated to transforming dreams into reality.">
	<TheHeader />

    <PortfolioHero
                category="Branding"
                projectName="Majestic Jade"
                projectCover="/assets/images/portfolio/jade/cover.webp"
                dataProject={[
                    ['Client', 'Jade, coordinadora de eventos'],
                    ['location', 'Ramos Arizpe, Coahuila MX'],
                    ['Date', 'January 2024'],
                    ['Role', 'Creative Director']
                ]}
                ></PortfolioHero>

    <section class="fh-portfolio-section">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="row pt-6 pb-6">
				<div class="col-12 col-lg-4" data-aos="fade-right">
					<h2>I.</h2>
				</div>
				<div class="col-12 col-lg-8" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-delay="400">
                    <h2>Understanding<br>the Context</h2>
					<p>Jade is a Mexican event coordination agency dedicated to transforming dreams into reality. They specialize in creating extraordinary social events that are as unique as their clients.</p>
                    <p>To bring the event coordinator's vision to life, I used a mind map as a starting point. This exercise helped me identify the key visual elements that would convey the values of empathy, commitment, and elegance, which are essential to her business.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

    <PauseSection image="/assets/images/portfolio/jade/analysis.webp" />

    <section class="fh-portfolio-section">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="row pt-6 pb-6">
				<div class="col-12 col-lg-4" data-aos="fade-right">
					<h2>II.</h2>
				</div>
				<div class="col-12 col-lg-8" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-delay="400">
                    <h2>Capturing Essence in Design</h2>
					<p>The primary goal was to visually represent Jade's core values: elegance, empathy, and commitment. This was achieved through a combination of refined typography, harmonious color palettes, and meticulous design elements. The logo's typography and structure reflect a dedication to detail and craftsmanship, while the intertwined "O" in "Coordinaci√≥n" symbolizes unity and partnership.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

    <PortfolioBigOne image="/assets/images/portfolio/jade/typo.webp"/>

    <PortfolioTwoImages imageOne="/assets/images/portfolio/jade/jade-flyer.webp" imageTwo="/assets/images/portfolio/jade/jade-cards.webp" />

    <section class="fh-portfolio-section">
		<div class="container">
			<div class="row pt-6 pb-6">
				<div class="col-12 col-lg-4" data-aos="fade-right">
					<h2>III.</h2>
				</div>
				<div class="col-12 col-lg-8" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-delay="400">
                    <h2>Jade: A Timeless Inspiration</h2>
                    <p>Jade, a precious stone with deep cultural significance in the Americas, will be the inspiration for a new logo design. The logo will feature a versatile green color palette to reflect jade's natural hues, complemented by gray for contrast. Gold foil will be used to enhance the logo's appearance and ensure its visibility on dark backgrounds.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

    <PortfolioTwoImages imageOne="/assets/images/portfolio/jade/colors.webp" imageTwo="/assets/images/portfolio/jade/stationery.webp" />

    <section class="fh-portfolio-section">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row pt-6 pb-6">
                <div class="col-12 col-lg-4" data-aos="fade-right">
                    <h2>IV.</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="col-12 col-lg-8" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-delay="400">
                    <h2>Conclusions</h2>
                    <p>It was a privilege to collaborate with Jade on creating such a sophisticated and elegant visual identity. Inspired by the timeless beauty of jade, we developed a versatile image that has been incredibly well-received on social media. Seeing our creation come to life in various formats is extremely rewarding.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <PauseSection image="/assets/images/portfolio/jade/back-jade.webp" />

    <PhilosophySection picture="/assets/images/portfolio/behance.webp">
        <Fragment slot="philosophy-content">
            <h2 class="black">Discover the Process</h2>
			<p>The magic behind a great logo lies in the details. Join me on Behance and discover my passion for graphic design.</p>
            <a href="https://bit.ly/3X2pArV" class="outline" target="_blank">Project in Behance Portfolio</a>
        </Fragment>
    </PhilosophySection>

    <ContactSection />

    <Menu />
</MainLayout>